text: Sunny (born June 11, 2012) is a pet dog of the Obama family, the 44th presidential family of the United States. Sunny is a female Portuguese Water Dog who was a First Dog of the United States along with Bo. Sunny was first seen through First Lady Michelle Obama's Twitter account on August 19, 2013. ==References== Category:2012 births Category:Obama family Category:United States presidential dogs
